'''Dr. Goyle''' is a psychiatrist at [[Grey Sloan Memorial Hospital]].

==History==
Dr. Goyle was called to talk to [[Casey Hedges]] when [[Jo Wilson]] suspected that she was faking her son's illness. She told him that she wasn't and explained the changes in Parker's behavior to convince them.

==Career==
Dr. Goyle is a psychiatrist at [[Grey Sloan Memorial Hospital]].
